## ğŸ“Š Dataset Overview

| Column                        | Description                                           |
|-------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| `Provider`                   | BNPL company (e.g., Klarna, Affirm)                   |
| `Year`                       | Year of data (2020â€“2024)                              |
| `Region`                     | Global region (US, EU, APAC)                          |
